Interactive Box Plot

Source: vignettes/boxly.Rmd
boxly.Rmd
library(boxly)
meta <- meta_boxly(
  boxly_adsl,
  boxly_adlb,
  population_term = "apat",
  observation_term = "wk12",
  observation_subset = AVISITN <= 12 & !is.na(CHG)
)
outdata <- prepare_boxly(meta)
outdata
